    title: 'Question 1',
    content:
      'Find the number of ways in which twelve different baseball cards can be\ngiven to Emily, Harry, John and Olivia, if Emily is to receive $5$\ncards, Harry is to receive $3$ cards, John is to receive $3$ cards and\nOlivia is to receive $1$ card (in that order).',
