      'Let $f(x) = x^3$ and $g(x) = 2x - 1$, for $x \\in \\mathbb{R}$.\n\n- Find $g^{-1}(x)$. <span class="marks">[2]</span>\n\n- Find $(g\\circ f)(x)$. <span class="marks">[2]</span>\n\n- Solve the equation $(g\\circ f)(x) = 0$. <span class="marks">[2]</span>\n\n',
