      'Let $f(x) = x^3 + 1$ and $g(x) = x-2$, for $x \\in \\mathbb{R}$.\n\n- Find $f(2)$. <span class="marks">[2]</span>\n\n- Find $f^{-1}(x)$. <span class="marks">[2]</span>\n\n- Solve $(f\\circ g)(x) = 0$. <span class="marks">[3]</span>\n\n',
